title: The Boxy Crew
description: On repeat. Our boxy crew is so versatile, it can’t be played out. Made with perfectly good cutting waste, otherwise destined for a landfill, and blended with the softest organic cotton- you’ll never guess this tee was made from scraps. Complete with a worn-in wash, from non-toxic and low impact dyes, this tee is a hit.

title: The Relaxed V
description: So chill. Our V neck earned its name for its laid-back shape. Its super soft fabric, made with eco-friendly dyes, gives a lived-in look that’s easy to dress up or down. Made of organic cotton and clean cutting waste, meant for a landfill, this recycled tee is as good for you as it is for the planet.

title: The Long Sleeve Tee
description: Not a clinger. Our loose fit, 90’s inspired long sleeve, gives you the space to do you. Its breathable fabric, made of recycled and organic cotton, is perfect for those throw on and go days. Free from toxic dyes, our super soft feel and vintagy wash is one of a kind. Warning, you may get attached.
